ChangelogDescription:
__**New Features**__

*• Added codes system, redeem codes.*
*• Added dev command to add new codes to the system*
*• Added new incense system, enable for 5x spawn chance.*
*• Added market system with 2 items (More coming)*
*• Added new welcome message when inviting the bot.*
*• Added auctions system, auction away Pokémons to other users.*

__**Changed Features**__

*• Revamped some Developer only commands for easier usage.*
*• Added battles leaderboard, display most battles won.*
